And, oh, look!
There's free grilled cheese.

16
00:00:39,505 --> 00:00:40,891
Okay, ground rules.

17
00:00:40,908 --> 00:00:42,022
Stop with the chatty,

18
00:00:42,037 --> 00:00:43,463
don't stand so close to me,

19
